.onepoundwebhosting.co.uk/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=42&amp;promocode=LEB50XEN\" target=\"_blank\">Direct signup link here</a></p><ul><li>512MB memory/512MB swap</li><li>40GB RAID10 storage</li><li>300GB/month data transfer @ 100mbit</li><li>4 x Dual XEON Quad Core cores</li><li>Xen/SolusVM</li><li>1 x IPv4</li></ul><p>The same offer is also <a title=\"OnePoundWebHosting Offers posted on LowEndTalk.com\" href=\"http://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/2023/uk-512mb-xen-50-off-recurring-onepoundwebhosting-offer-extended-with-increased-bandwidth\" target=\"_blank\">posted on LET</a> and <a title=\"OnePoundWebHosting Offers posted on WebHostingTalk.com\" href=\"http://www.webhostingtalk.com/showthread.php?t=1139488\" target=\"_blank\">WHT</a> (same discount, different coupon code). They have Supermicro servers with <a title=\"ServerHouse UK\" href=\"http://www.serverhouse.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\">ServerHouse</a> in Fareham, Hampshire UK. No test IP has been provided but I believe its the same as <a title=\"OnePoundWebHosting \u2013 \u00a36.30/Quarter 128MB Xen VPS in UK\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/onepoundwebhosting-6-30quarter-128mb-xen-vps-in-uk/\" target=\"_blank\">previously posted</a> (test IP: 195.49.147.100). It is a registered UK company since 2006 (company number: 05886975).&nbsp;Please take a moment to read their <a title=\"Terms and Conditions\" href=\"http://www.onepoundwebhosting.co.uk/terms.php\" target=\"_blank\">Terms and Conditions</a> and <a title=\"Service Level Agreement\" href=\"http://www.onepoundwebhosting.co.uk/sla.php\" target=\"_blank\">SLA</a>.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-